PN,31701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780711405
OL,3,CIranian journalist stabbed on Tehran's
OL,4,Corders says police did not act on
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FAn Iranian television presenter
OL,8,Fstabbed in a knife attack commissioned
OL,9,Fby the Tehran regime says police
OL,10,Ffailed to connect a series of warnings
OL,11,Fand suspicious incidents which, he
OL,12,Fbelieves, might have prevented the
OL,13,Fviolent assault against him.
OL,15,FIran International journalist Pouria
OL,16,FZeraati was left bleeding in the
OL,17,Fstreet after he was attacked by
OL,18,Fproxies of the Iranian regime outside
OL,19,Fhis home in Wimbledon, south-west
OL,20,FLondon, on March 29 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780711405
OL,3,CIranian journalist stabbed on Tehran's
OL,4,Corders says police did not act on
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FZeraati, an anchor at the Persian-
OL,8,Flanguage broadcaster Iran
OL,9,FInternational, said he was "shocked"
OL,10,Fto discover that his wife had
OL,11,Funwittingly recorded one of his future
OL,12,Fattackers carrying out reconnaissance
OL,13,Foutside their London home more than a
OL,14,Fyear before the stabbing.
OL,16,FZeraati's wife filmed two men after
OL,17,Fnoticing them behaving suspiciously
OL,18,Foutside the couple's apartment block
OL,19,Fin March 2023, dressed in black with
OL,20,Ftheir hoods up and wandering across
OL,21,Fthe driveway.
OL,26,@qD@\OUqD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780711405
OL,3,CIranian journalist stabbed on Tehran's
OL,4,Corders says police did not act on
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FShe shared the footage with police,
OL,8,Fwho detained and questioned the men,
OL,9,Fbut concluded there was no evidence
OL,10,Flinking them to the threats from
OL,11,FTehran against Zeraati.
OL,13,FBut in March 2024, it was one of those
OL,14,Fmen, 25-year-old George Stana, who
OL,15,Freturned to the same address as part
OL,16,Fof a group that stabbed Zeraati three
OL,17,Ftimes in the leg - an attack
OL,18,Fcommissioned by Iran's Islamic
OL,19,FRevolutionary Guard Corps.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780711405
OL,3,CIranian journalist stabbed on Tehran's
OL,4,Corders says police did not act on
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FStana, alongside fellow Romanian
OL,8,FNandito Badea, was found guilty on
OL,9,FFriday of attacking Zeraati at
OL,10,FWoolwich Crown Court.
OL,12,FIt is believed to be the first
OL,13,Fsuccessful prosecution in the UK
OL,14,Fconnected to an attack by criminals
OL,15,Facting on behalf of the Iranian regime.
OL,17,FZeraati worked for Iran International,
OL,18,Fa competitor of the state broadcaster,
OL,19,Fwhich the Iranian regime designated a
OL,20,Fterrorist organisation and branded "a
OL,21,Fnetwork of spies".
OL,26,@|D@dOU}D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
