PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780711405
OL,3,CIranian journalist stabbed on Tehran's
OL,4,Corders says police did not act on
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe Persian-language news outlet was
OL,13,Fbased in Chiswick, west London, until
OL,14,FFebruary 2023, when threats made
OL,15,Fagainst the network, its employees and
OL,16,Ftheir families led to it relocating
OL,17,Ftemporarily to Washington DC.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
