CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780711405
OL,3,CIranian journalist stabbed on Tehran's
OL,4,Corders says police did not act on
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FIn an exclusive interview with ITV
OL,8,FNews, Zeraati described the moments
OL,9,Fafter the attack as "the worst moment"
OL,10,Fof his life.
OL,12,FRecalling the attack, Zeraati said he
OL,13,Fwondered, "will I be alive in the next
OL,14,Ffew seconds"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780711405
OL,3,CIranian journalist stabbed on Tehran's
OL,4,Corders says police did not act on
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,F"I think I will never forget this
OL,8,Fmoment in my whole life, not only
OL,9,Fbecause of what happened to me - that
OL,10,Fthey stabbed me in the leg - (but)
OL,11,Fbecause in those two, three seconds
OL,12,Fwhile it happened, all I was thinking
OL,13,Fwas, where is he going to stab? Is he
OL,14,Fgoing to stab my neck? My heart? My
OL,15,Fkidney? Will I be alive in the next
OL,16,Ffew seconds or not? This is a moment
OL,17,Fthat you don't want to experience in
OL,18,Fyour life."
OL,26,@rD@^pmrD@bpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780711405
OL,3,CIranian journalist stabbed on Tehran's
OL,4,Corders says police did not act on
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FZeraati and his wife only realised the
OL,8,Fsignificance of the footage recorded
OL,9,Fin 2023 - and its links to the
OL,10,Fsubsequent attack - when it was played
OL,11,Fto jurors. The couple had barely given
OL,12,Fthe video any thought during the three
OL,13,Fyears since it was filmed.
OL,15,FZeraati's wife filmed two men after
OL,16,Fnoticing them behaving suspiciously
OL,17,Foutside the couple's apartment block
OL,18,Fin March 2023.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780711405
OL,3,CIranian journalist stabbed on Tehran's
OL,4,Corders says police did not act on
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,F"That's the most shocking part of the
OL,8,Ftrial to me, which I didn't have any
OL,9,Fidea about before the trial. It's
OL,10,Fanother incident, in March 2023. It
OL,11,Fhappened exactly a year and four weeks
OL,12,Fbefore the actual attack happened in
OL,13,F2024, 29th March."
OL,15,F"There are two people in our area, on
OL,16,Four road, trying to go around
OL,17,Fdifferent places doing surveillance.
OL,19,F"They entered our block as well.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780711405
OL,3,CIranian journalist stabbed on Tehran's
OL,4,Corders says police did not act on
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,F"Because we had a balcony and a window
OL,8,Ftowards the communal garden on the
OL,9,Fground floor - so we had a view of the
OL,10,Fdriveway, whoever is entering the
OL,11,Fdriveway and we had a view of who is
OL,12,Fexiting the gate."
OL,14,F"My wife noticed two strange people
OL,15,Ftrying to get into the driveway, and a
OL,16,Ffew minutes later they tried to leave
OL,17,Fthe building. So she filmed them,
OL,18,Fbecause since 2022 we had been
OL,19,Freceiving threats against us."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780711405
OL,3,CIranian journalist stabbed on Tehran's
OL,4,Corders says police did not act on
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FZeraati says the police shouldn't have
OL,8,Faccepted the explanation given by the
OL,9,Fpair after they were arrested.
OL,11,F"At least one of the scenarios they
OL,12,Fneeded to consider was that this was
OL,13,Flinked to Pouria," he said.
OL,15,FHe added: "(We) filmed it ourselves,
OL,16,F(we) reported it to you, you took a
OL,17,Fstatement from my wife. It wasn't just
OL,18,Fthe videos they took, they took a
OL,19,Fstatement from my wife as well. And
OL,20,Fnothing was communicated afterwards.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@RO]wD@KOUwD@LpmwD@OpnxD@ApmxD@
OL,26,ADpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780711405
OL,3,CIranian journalist stabbed on Tehran's
OL,4,Corders says police did not act on
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,F"I hope they take it seriously ` and I
OL,8,Fhope not because of this interview `
OL,9,Fbut because it has already changed the
OL,10,Fway different departments communicate."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780711405
OL,3,CIranian journalist stabbed on Tehran's
OL,4,Corders says police did not act on
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FDet Supt Kris Wright, Commander of
OL,8,FSpecialist Operations for the
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police, told ITV News:
OL,10,F"At the time, it was treated as it
OL,11,Fpresented, of a suspicious incident in
OL,12,Fa communal area. Local policing
OL,13,Fprovided an excellent response to it,
OL,14,Fand it's only with the investigation
OL,15,Finto the stabbing that we were able to
OL,16,Flook backwards, and realise in context
OL,17,Fthat it was hostile reconnaissance and
OL,18,Fattack planning attacks in the UK."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780711405
OL,3,CIranian journalist stabbed on Tehran's
OL,4,Corders says police did not act on
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FZeraati says the failure of officers
OL,8,Fto act on the earlier incident was
OL,9,Fespecially difficult to understand
OL,10,Fgiven that it came during an
OL,11,Fintensifying campaign of intimidation
OL,12,Fagainst journalists working for Iran
OL,13,FInternational, a channel viewed by the
OL,14,FIranian regime as hostile.
OL,16,FOne month earlier, the broadcaster was
OL,17,Fforced to abandon its west London
OL,18,Fheadquarters after receiving "credible
OL,19,Fthreats" linked to Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780711405
OL,3,CIranian journalist stabbed on Tehran's
OL,4,Corders says police did not act on
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FIn Tehran, posters had appeared
OL,8,Fcarrying Zeraati's image alongside the
OL,9,Fwords: "Wanted: Dead or alive."
OL,11,FIn 2022, with the protest movement in
OL,12,FIran growing in the wake of the death
OL,13,Fin police custody of Mahasa Amini and
OL,14,Fthe regime under pressure, Zeraati's
OL,15,Fwife was stopped in the street and
OL,16,Fgiven a chilling warning by a stranger
OL,17,Fas she walked through west London.
OL,26,@qD@HOUqD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780711405
OL,3,CIranian journalist stabbed on Tehran's
OL,4,Corders says police did not act on
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,F"She herself received a credible
OL,8,Fthreat in 2022 when she was going to
OL,9,Fthe gym," Pouria said. "A motorcyclist
OL,10,Fapproached her with two riders. One of
OL,11,Fthem said in Farsi: 'We know where you
OL,12,Flive, we know what your husband does,
OL,13,Fwe are going to come after you and
OL,14,Fkill you very soon."
OL,16,F"At the time we were moved out to a
OL,17,Fsafe place for a few days, it was
OL,18,Fduring the 'Women, Life, Freedom'
OL,19,Fmovement in 2022"
OL,26,@qD@IO]qD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31717
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780711405
OL,3,CIranian journalist stabbed on Tehran's
OL,4,Corders says police did not act on
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,F"And after that the police installed
OL,8,Fsensors in our flat, they took some
OL,9,Fmeasurements and gave us panic
OL,10,Fbuttons."
OL,12,F"It was obvious to the police that we
OL,13,Fare at risk. As an Iranian journalist
OL,14,Fand a journalist working for Iran
OL,15,FInternational."
OL,17,FZeraati says his panic buttons were
OL,18,Fwithdrawn by Scotland Yard because he
OL,19,Fwas no longer judged to be at a level
OL,20,Fof risk that warranted the extra
OL,21,Fequipment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31718
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780711405
OL,3,CIranian journalist stabbed on Tehran's
OL,4,Corders says police did not act on
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FResponding to Pouria's claims that
OL,8,Fpolice withdrew his panic alarm before
OL,9,Fthe attack, Scotland Yard said it
OL,10,Fwould not comment on the protective
OL,11,Fmeasures provided to individuals.
OL,13,FBadea, 21, and Stana had both denied
OL,14,Fthe attack.
OL,16,FBadea, a former professional
OL,17,Ffootballer, told the court he was in
OL,18,FWimbledon on March 29 to carry out
OL,19,Fsurveillance on a man who was
OL,20,Fsuspected of having an affair with
OL,21,Fanother man's wife.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31719
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780711405
OL,3,CIranian journalist stabbed on Tehran's
OL,4,Corders says police did not act on
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FHe claimed a man called David Andrei,
OL,8,Fwho is not a defendant in the trial,
OL,9,Fcame up from behind and stabbed
OL,10,FZeraati in the thigh.
OL,12,FThe defendants headed to Heathrow
OL,13,FAirport on the day of the alleged
OL,14,Fattack and fled to Geneva in
OL,15,FSwitzerland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
